race.comment: PAW MAUD (4) flew the lids from out wide with a slick early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fourth (23.29) over 410m at Horsham. Better than last start and worth following up. DR. EDDIE (2) took a tumble when crowded up close to the inside last time over 510m at Sale. No luck latest and gets chance to atone. JUNIOR'S MATE (7) has been out of the placings the last couple but was a Grade 5 winner (26.22) three back at Warragul. Can feature with the right run. PAW ILLABO (1) has strong credentials from this draw. Something for the Multiples: HEY PRESTO (6)
